{"tid":1639330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【勇武港女】教你如何合法交稅/差餉/水費交到政府蝕錢","createTime":"2019-10-08T14:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T01:22:55.000Z","uid":88241,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2489fdeeff57d90b394d7271a6d857c659270ebe","tid":1639330,"uid":88241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:54:35.000Z","msg":"原來咁多人唔識做automation . 等我IT 狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />教大家點樣可以做自動<br />\n可以用黎買演唱會飛...我eason 都係咁買到既!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買演唱會飛原post <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1637669/page/102\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1637669/page/102</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIT 狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />教大家點樣自動 如果用chrome/firefox 既巴絲可以照住做<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.去裝一個imarco 既plugin, 記住去返GOOGLE 裝</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/imacros-for-chrome/cplklnmnlbnpmjogncfgfijoopmnlemp?hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fimacros-for-chrome%2Fcplklnmnlbnpmjogncfgfijoopmnlemp%3Fhl%3Den&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=bfa21744\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/imacros-for-chrome/cplklnmnlbnpmjogncfgfijoopmnlemp?hl=en</a><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kt1wubE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKt1wubE.png&h=07f270a4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.裝完就會多左個icon (藍色齒輪), 再去你交費用既網頁 </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8AUrYn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8AUrYn.png&h=2a08cdd7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3.點一下藍色齒輪去mange &gt; setting &gt; player setting &gt;改成 slow</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJOfbp0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJOfbp0.png&h=05a7d1a6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/duz90im.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fduz90im.png&h=540e6fc2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4.點一下 Record-&gt; Record Marco 就可以開始自動錄製auto script</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ex6THwG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEx6THwG.png&h=044a954d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5.錄完可以按play 試一下., 無問題既話可以set max loop 次數就搞掂</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lpr8wp0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpr8wp0.png&h=c2b81de5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae5c11cdbbdf632076b3ff0f28fcc523e73b21d","tid":1639330,"uid":88241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"f8a865cfda5925db823aa675ee97fb5f3f7068d8","tid":1639330,"uid":88241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:56:03.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"d02df7b49c99396b9f87c7a0e27a682b9bc4ad69","tid":1639330,"uid":88241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:56:13.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"1bd76d5fe23a703b607d73722ce5a9e27a695ec7","tid":1639330,"uid":88241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"845c3fd5c4f4ae3808b5d454cf9ccc381b16f284","tid":1639330,"uid":308178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:58:01.000Z","msg":"IT狗，你的資訊真的很有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f47ac081230b3524659947b63c4b2839076a5a","tid":1639330,"uid":41656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:01:12.000Z","ms